-- Gillard to Announce New Ministry `Very Soon' Amid Talks on Kevin Rudd Role
-- Robert Fenner
-- 2010-06-26T22:58:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-26/gillard-to-announce-new-ministry-very-soon-amid-talks-on-kevin-rudd-role.html

          
          
             Australian Prime Minister Julia
Gillard will announce her new ministry “very soon” as she
seeks to speak to predecessor Kevin Rudd about what role he will
play. Gillard declined to give a specific date for the
announcement in an interview with Channel 9 television today.  
          
          


  


        